page.title: 06Alton Schoolday (1)
page.content: I woke up at 7.30am, got out of bed and put the blinds up and put my clothes on.I went downstairs into the kitchen,poured some milk on my Rice Krispies and sugar and ate them.I got my school stuff ready after breakfast and went into my room.At 8.45am it was time to go to school.I got into the car and arrived at school at 8.57am. Into school at 9.00am.When we got into the classroom we had to go to assembly.After assembly we had to do some Maths.At 10.05am it was P.E time and we played volleyball.Then at 10.40 it was break_time.During break we played tennis ball football and King He.Then after break we did History until 12.00pm.Lunch time at last!
